"Choisir <span class=\"menuchoice\"> <span class=\"guimenu\">Machine</"
"span>&nbsp;▸ <span class=\"guimenuitem\">Configuration...</span></span>."

#. type: Bullet: '  1. '
msgid "In the **Name and operating system** screen, specify:"
